רקע / râqa‛ / raw-kah'
=== Etymology ===

A primitive root; 
=== Verb ===
to pound the earth (as a sign of passion); by analogy to expand (by hammering); by implication to overlay (with thin sheets of metal): - [[beat]], make broad, spread abroad (forth, over, out, into plates), stamp, stretch.